{"tid":534962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攻陷沙田！強國師奶萬寧掃貨兩粒鐘 父子門口鋤啤呆等","createTime":"2018-01-20T10:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T03:17:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":146,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"809893c309d51697961c8d941777a8f3a3e9b5c1","tid":534962,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180120/large/1516439744_7dbd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180120%2Flarge%2F1516439744_7dbd.png&h=de50e650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨近農曆新年，大批內地客趁周末拖篋來港，到沙田新城市廣場掃貨，大手添置日用品、化妝品和零食，區內不少店舖外都出現排隊人龍。<br />\n<br />\n來自廣州的何先生和6歲兒子在萬寧門外席地而坐，兩父子被6大袋膠袋包圍，只顧在行李篋上玩啤牌。何先生解釋，太太已在萬寧逗留了2小時添購日用品，包括沐浴露、洗髮乳等，「小孩都悶了」，父子唯有玩啤牌解悶消磨時間。何稱今次來港是為辦年貨兼購物，預算花費3至4萬元人民幣，目標是買金飾、手錶和首飾等。<br />\n<br />\n來自惠州的陳小姐和友人來香港一日遊順道購物，她稱每年都會來港購買日用品、化妝和護膚品，以往曾到上水、旺角，聽朋友介紹沙田商場多商舖、貨品齊全故特意前來購物，「但我現在有點後悔」，她指商場內的商舖分佈太遠，種類不集中，「走來走的，累呀」。陳小姐稱今早11時來到沙田，一直血拼到下午3時，單在萬寧已花了約3,000元。她承認受惠於人民幣匯率升值，來港購物比較划算，雖然香港不是太多商戶支援內地流行的支付寶交易，「但我沒所謂，可用可不用」。<br />\n<br />\n除了日常用品以外，不少化妝品專櫃都迫滿人，部分名店專櫃更要派籌給客人輪流付錢。來自深圳的周小姐花了500多元買2支唇膏，她稱雖然香港買化妝品較貴，但既然是要塗在臉上，在專櫃購買品質較令人安心。<br />\n<br />\n沙田新城市廣場的apple store門外亦有近70人排隊。來自湖南的余小姐稱計劃添置一部iPhone8 Plus自用。另一名內地旅客則指希望在新一年用新手機，今次打算購買一部iPhone X自用，「剛開售時搶不到」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180120/large/1516439488_0d4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180120%2Flarge%2F1516439488_0d4a.png&h=1ff187e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180120/large/1516439490_d9ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180120%2Flarge%2F1516439490_d9ca.png&h=4a433a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180120/large/1516440074_8473.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180120%2Flarge%2F1516440074_8473.png&h=8913326c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180120/57732336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F57732336&d=asHCf3I7mV5Ffg3ruDbINzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5a817d68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F57732336&h=e3966212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180120/57732336</a>"},{"pid":"2cfea5355a5a8bd4be6fb86a5ddec1a590df5ee3","tid":534962,"uid":85819,"like":47,"dislike":218,"score":-171,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63f1fa380459fc273f777ff64c53e888f1151c35","tid":534962,"uid":25900,"like":138,"dislike":10,"score":128,"quote":{"pid":"2cfea5355a5a8bd4be6fb86a5ddec1a590df5ee3","tid":534962,"uid":85819,"like":47,"dislike":218,"score":-171,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:00:46.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"58cc589811403b14e05d16330717c46b5998fb0a","tid":534962,"uid":38671,"like":256,"dislike":6,"score":250,"quote":{"pid":"63f1fa380459fc273f777ff64c53e888f1151c35","tid":534962,"uid":25900,"like":138,"dislike":10,"score":128,"quote":{"pid":"2cfea5355a5a8bd4be6fb86a5ddec1a590df5ee3","tid":534962,"uid":85819,"like":47,"dislike":218,"score":-171,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:00:46.000Z","msg":"On9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"自由行出現之前香港係漁村（好似係）"},{"pid":"1116ea4b4c8f4a40dc7e2dd9d3a6ee6fdd8bf026","tid":534962,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲天下<im